image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure document, specifically an OGE Form 278e, detailing various business entities, their ownership structure, and the roles of individuals or other entities within them. The document is for Donald J. Trump and is page A17 of 47.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form information and the filer's name. The main body is a list of entities, identified by a reference number. Each entry details ownership percentages, the names of the owners, their roles, and any ownership interests the entity has in other entities.
